He makes a decision that will shape the future

488
00:42:59,290 --> 00:43:01,180
决定了整个罗马帝国的未来
Of the Roman Empire.

489
00:43:03,300 --> 00:43:06,930
"我久久期盼的时刻终于到来
"The time is arrived I have long hoped for,

490
