"That I might obtain the salvation of God."

492
00:43:20,910 --> 00:43:26,080
西方世界最强大的人接受了洗礼
The most powerful man in the western world is baptized.

493
00:43:27,990 --> 00:43:29,960
数百年来
For hundreds of years,

494
00:43:29,960 --> 00:43:32,790
基督教一直被罗马帝国欺凌
Christianity was being quelled,

495
00:43:32,790 --> 00:43:35,990
镇压甚至是迫害
and put down by the Roman Empire, even persecuted.

